==Gallery== <gallery> File:Taiwan Grand Shrine.jpg|A [[postcard]] issued by the [[:en:Governor-General of Taiwan|Governor-General of Taiwan]] of Taiwan Grand Shrine. The [[:en:Imperial Seal of Japan|Imperial Seal]] is visible in the upper-right section. File:Taiwan_(Japanese_Colony)_1932_bank_note_-_10_yen_(front).jpg|Taiwan banknotes (10 yen banknotes) during the Japanese colonial era with the Taiwan Grand Shrine printed File:1923rd year 日本皇太子裕仁訪拜臺灣神社_Japanese_Crown_Prince_Hirohito_on_the_way_to_Taiwan_Grand_Shrine.jpg|Prince Hirohito visits the Taiwan Grand Shrine during the Crown Prince Hirohito's visit to Taiwan (April 17, 1923) File:Copper cattle of Taiwan Jinja.JPG|This copper bull was originally located at Taiwan Grand Shrine but was moved to in front of [[National Taiwan Museum]] after the end of World War II. </gallery>
